<section id="about">
  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <p style="text-align:center;">
    NMH Hospital is a trusted healthcare center in Vaniyambadi, Tamil Nadu,
    delivering quality medical care with experienced doctors and modern facilities.
  </p>
